{"cursor":"7941","size":15,"audio":[],"currentlang":"en","article":"\n]] 'Platform shoes' (also known as 'disco boots' and 'triangle heels') are\nshoes, boots, or sandals with thick soles at least four inches in height. They\nare often made of cork, plastic, rubber, or wood (wooden-soled platform shoes\nare, technically, also clogs). Platform shoes have been worn, for reasons such\nas fashion or added height, in various cultures since the Ancient era.\n","linknr":311,"url":"Platform_shoe","recorded":1362578997,"links":28,"instances":["footwear","footwear","disambiguation","material","magazine"],"pdf":[],"categories":["Shoes","Boots","Sandals","1970s fashion","History of fashion","1980s fashion","2010s fashion"],"headings":["History","See also","Notable wearers","References","External links"],"image":["//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/50px-Question_book-new.svg.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Ellie821heel.JPG/220px-Ellie821heel.JPG","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/05/Platform_Sandal_wood_Buffalo_brown-bright.jpg/250px-Platform_Sandal_wood_Buffalo_brown-bright.jpg","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/74/Platform_boot_Buffalo_black.jpg/250px-Platform_boot_Buffalo_black.jpg","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/15/Acrylic_Heels.jpg/200px-Acrylic_Heels.jpg","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Commons-logo.svg/30px-Commons-logo.svg.png","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/vector/images/search-ltr.png?303-4","//bits.wikimedia.org/images/wikimedia-button.png","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/poweredby_mediawiki_88x31.png